@startuml

actor Student
actor Instructor
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant "File Storage\nService" as FileStorage
participant "Email & Notification\nService" as Notification

' Login & Navigation Flow
Student -> Frontend: Log In to LMS
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: Authenticate User
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Login Successful
deactivate Backend
Student -> Frontend: Navigate to Course Dashboard
Frontend -> Backend: Request Assignment List
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Display Assignments
deactivate Backend
Student -> Frontend: Select Assignment & Review Details
deactivate Frontend

' Deadline Check Flow
Frontend -> Backend: Check Submission Deadline
activate Frontend
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Deadline Status (Open / Late / Closed)
deactivate Backend
Frontend --> Student: Display Deadline Status
deactivate Frontend

' File Upload Flow
Student -> Frontend: Upload Submission File (PDF / ZIP / Link)
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: Submit File
activate Backend
Backend -> FileStorage: Store Submission File
activate FileStorage
FileStorage --> Backend: File Stored Successfully
deactivate FileStorage
Backend --> Frontend: File Accepted
deactivate Backend

' Record & Confirm Flow
Backend --> Frontend: Submission Confirmed & Status Updated
Frontend --> Student: View Submission Status on Dashboard
deactivate Frontend

' Notification Flow
Backend -> Notification: Send Submission Receipt to Student
activate Notification
Backend -> Notification: Notify Instructor of New Submission
Notification --> Student: Receive Confirmation Email
Notification --> Instructor: Submission Queued for Grading
deactivate Notification

@enduml
